          alt="Electrical panel upgrade with organized breakers and labeling"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </figure>
      <h3>Panel modernization for future capacity</h3>
      <p>
        Upgrade focused on capacity, cleaner breaker layout, and a panel
        directory that makes future service calls faster.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist checklist--compact">
        <li>Cleaner labeling and circuit organization</li>
        <li>Room for EV charging, remodel loads, or equipment additions</li>
        <li>
          Finished result built for serviceability, not just inspection minimums
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="case-study">
      <figure>
        <img
          src="/Past_work_webp/Exterior%20Light%20Fixtures.webp"
          width="2048"
          height="1536"
          alt="Exterior light fixtures installed neatly on a home"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </figure>
      <h3>Lighting work that supports the look of the property</h3>
      <p>
        Fixture and lighting upgrades where placement, finish quality, and
        alignment matter as much as the power itself.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist checklist--compact">
        <li>Better curb appeal and usability</li>
        <li>Cleaner final fixture placement</li>
        <li>Useful for remodels, entries, patios, and whole-home refreshes</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="case-study">
      <figure>
        <img
          src="/Past_work_webp/Control%20Cabinet.webp"
          width="1536"
          height="2048"
          alt="Organized control cabinet wiring in a commercial environment"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </figure>
      <h3>Control and conduit work in active facilities</h3>
      <p>
        Organized commercial work where readable terminations, routing clarity,
        and long-term maintainability matter.
      </p>
      <ul class="checklist checklist--compact">
        <li>Useful in shops, mixed-use, and light industrial settings</li>
        <li>Supports troubleshooting and future changes</li>
        <li>Built for the next service visit too</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

